</emphasis>
The species name is a Latin adjective (
<emphasis box="[775,1015,835,859]" italics="true" pageId="92" pageNumber="93">rubifasciatus, -a, -um</emphasis>
= with a red stripe).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
